{"tid":271147,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"日本豐胸背心一秒變警鐘胸？男人着都work！","createTime":"2017-06-05T00:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T02:31:15.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"242f17fb804648994941524630c5bceac3edb7fb","tid":271147,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T00:05:21.000Z","msg":"英國《鏡報》早前報道，日本一件產品幫你免開刀豐胸。說的是這件神奇背心，日本amazon都有售，我們就馬上買件試真身。<br />\n<br />\n這件豐胸背心有大中小尺碼，售價約190港元，都頗貴。原理是透過格子圖案的大小，塑造上圍撐開背心的錯覺，到底實物上身是否有效？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【正常尺碼：Work!】</strong><br />\n找來上圍屬正常尺碼女記者實試，穿起普通黑色背心，沒很大睇頭是正常效果。換上視覺豐胸背心，馬上升級，有效！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【豐滿身形：更Work!】</strong><br />\n我們再用厚墊胸圍和缽仔糕，模仿上圍很睇頭的女生，測試穿效果會否更大。果然豐胸的視覺效果更誇張，簡直有逼爆螢幕的感覺！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【男生試穿：都Work!】</strong><br />\n想不到連男生穿也有升級效果，Steve馬上擁有42吋胸肌，效果誇張！<br />\n<strong><br />\n【試後感】</strong><br />\n測試員Sa：「我覺得這件衫上鏡效果很澎湃，但真人看十秒大家會否頭暈？這件衫要$190我不會買，$190我不如買個push up胸圍，還可穿其他衣服，這件衫設計很怪。」<br />\n<br />\n測試員Steve：「正面看誇張很多，特別透過鏡頭更強勁到凸出來般，不過側面看就變回正常。加上設計奇怪，應該不會有女生穿出街。」<br />\n<br />\n其實胸大都不一定美，還是自自然然最順眼，買來朋友派對玩玩就適合。<br />\n<br />\n記者：羅祖兒<br />\n攝影：王國輝<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496396734_1d5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496396734_1d5d.jpg&h=8a6b5f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本洗版創意之作──視覺豐胸背心，效果誇張。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496396735_fea6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496396735_fea6.png&h=ac9ac982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n視覚大胸の背心 約190港元<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496396738_cbd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496396738_cbd3.jpg&h=07d75df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【正常尺碼：Work!】換上視覺豐胸背心，馬上升級，有效！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496396740_702c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496396740_702c.jpg&h=19f117b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【豐滿身形：更Work!】上圍很睇頭的女生，簡直有逼爆mon的感覺！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496396741_f401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496396741_f401.jpg&h=4d49b090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【男生試穿：都Work!】男生也有升級效果，Steve馬上擁有42吋胸肌！<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170605/56774902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170605%2F56774902&d=FscGbLe7T1TTAA0VB6MmGP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=232e5a55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170605%2F56774902&h=336f3611\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170605/56774902</a>"},{"pid":"99f0b05c1f182669f2b33c3f8d444ca2fc3d6458","tid":271147,"uid":28515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T00:06:22.000Z","msg":"條女不錯"},{"pid":"60915a447a8cbcacff3555e2f6c1cf74104bf320","tid":271147,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"搵同一條女測兩次做咩9???"},{"pid":"1f8bced491a05c8fa659e294df51a75b2cba6a53","tid":271147,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵同一條女測兩次做咩9???</blockquote><br />\n我們再用厚墊胸圍和缽仔糕，模仿上圍很睇頭的女生"}]}